Usage: checkFPlanSpace [-help] [-clearMarker] [-outfile <string>] [-constraints <string> | -trackUtil <string>]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-clearMarker                   # Clear out markers on GUI. (bool, optional)
-constraints <string>          # -constraints <fileName> (string, optional)
-outfile <string>              # -outFile <fileName> (string, optional)
-trackUtil <string>            # -trackUtil <M1 0.0 M2 1.0 ...>
                               # (list, optional)